packDesc2022: overview of ontoProc resources

packDesc2022.Rd

packDesc2022: overview of ontoProc resources

Usage

packDesc2022

Format

data.frame instance

Note

Brief survey of functions available to load serialized ontology_index instances imported from OBO. Focus is on versions added in 2022.

Examples

data(packDesc2022)
head(packDesc2022)
#>   X            name nclass nprop nroots                                  datav
#> 1 1            caro    751    57     30 caro/releases/2022-02-18/caro-full.owl
#> 2 2    cellLineOnto  43596   204    110                                   <NA>
#> 3 3        cellOnto  17126   226    102                    releases/2022-08-16
#> 4 4 cellosaurusOnto 134841    21 134841                                   40.0
#> 5 5      chebi_full 162229    34     13                                    212
#> 6 6      chebi_lite 162229    32     13                                    212
#>   fmtv
